message.entry: REGIONPROPS3 needs a 3-D volumetric grayscale image, V as the second input argument to calculate ''{0}''.
PROPERTY must be a string or character vector.
Size of 3-D volumetric grayscale image, V doesn''t match size information found in the first input argument.
BW cannot have more than 3 dimensions.
The value of numel(CC.ImageSize) cannot be more than 3.
At least one label entry is not finite. Only finite labels are allowed.
The ''{0}'' property is not supported for code generation.
Optional properties must be a string or a character vector constant.
